			p Yes.
			p No information is stored or transmitted anywhere other than this page. As soon as you close the browser or refresh the page, all the data that you put into the page is deleted.
			p Want to verify? #[a(href="https://github.com/kenhoff/cashflow") You can check out all the code for this project on GitHub].
